OL,3,CFrench Open: Alcohol banned in stands
OL,4,Cafter player complaints
OL,6,FAlcohol has been banned in the stands
OL,7,Fat Roland Garros by French Open bosses
OL,8,Fafter a fan spat chewing gum at David
OL,9,FGoffin.
OL,11,FThe Belgian tennis player had just
OL,12,Fbeaten Frenchman Giovanni Mphetshi
OL,13,FPerricard - before hitting out at a
OL,14,Fparticularly boisterous crowd,
OL,15,Fclaiming one fan had spat gum at him.
OL,17,FAs a result, fans have been told they
OL,18,Fwill no longer be able to drink at
OL,19,Ftheir seat.
