OL,3,CFrench Open: Alcohol banned in stands
OL,4,Cafter player complaints
OL,6,FTournament boss Amelie Mauresmo said
OL,7,Fthat security measures have been
OL,8,Ftightened and umpires instructed to be
OL,9,Fstricter with the crowd during matches.
OL,11,F"Alcohol was until now authorised in
OL,12,Fthe stands. Now it's over," said
OL,13,FMauresmo.
OL,15,F"The umpires are really going to be
OL,16,Feven more strict to further respect to
OL,17,Fthe players and respect the game.
