OL,6,F"This is something that we're not
OL,7,Fgoing to tolerate, to overstep these
OL,8,Ftwo things. That's for sure. So
OL,9,Fumpires have quite an important role
OL,10,Fin this matter.
OL,12,F"And definitely in terms of security,
OL,13,Fwe're going to try to see which people
OL,14,Fis maybe making (trouble), because I
OL,15,Fthink it's a few individuals at some
OL,16,Fpoint that are overstepping."
OL,18,FMauresmo said that the person who spat
OL,19,Fgum at Goffin had not been identified
OL,20,Fand that no spectators had been
OL,21,Fejected from the tournament so far.
